summary: donuts! bright pink, teal, and purple, and ready to party. tbh this was made bc i wanted to mess with brushes and different...
caption:
donuts!

bright pink, teal, and purple, and ready to party. tbh this was made bc i wanted to mess with brushes and different shading methods i can do in medibang paint pro. i also recently learned how to make patterns and other stuff in medibang! putting it all together was a doozy tho. i love how these came out <3 and i hope you do too!~

pls donut steal, but feel free to use as a desktop/phone background! just like or rb. or dont. just. dont claim this art as ur own :3
